This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3563

A light color scheme with a purple-blue overall theme. Uses a light gray background, easy on the eyes and offers good contrast.

Examples using 10pt Consolas on Windows:

C++ & C: http://users.jyu.fi/~anhekalm/misc/amethyst_cpp_c.png
Haskell & LaTeX: http://users.jyu.fi/~anhekalm/misc/amethyst_hs_tex.png
Python & C#: http://users.jyu.fi/~anhekalm/misc/amethyst_py_cs.png

